text: Jeffrey Warren Daniels (born February 19, 1955) is an American actor. He was born in Athens, Georgia. He grew up in Chelsea, Michigan. Daniels starred in Something Wild, Terms of Endearment, Arachnophobia and Dumb and Dumber.
